{
  "stem": "5103.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was a lounge room-- a dining-- lounge-dining all in one and a kitchen-- and a toilet downstairs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then upstairs there were three rooms, one for my uncle and my grandfather with a double bed, one for the owners of the house, and one was like a small little bedroom with a dining table in it and six chairs.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in that room is where we lived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now upstairs was an attic, and in that attic was my father and my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then a little place for me as well to sleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So the whole thing was that these people had not wanted to hide a child in the first place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This was my parent's first hiding place and they'd been there all along.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so when I arrived there and my father and my mother cuddled me and everything, when that wore off they told me, [?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Corrie, ?] nobody speaks loud here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Everybody speaks in a whisper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You must never laugh loud, you must never cry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You must only say yes and no when you're spoken to, and you must be a very good girl.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Otherwise you can't stay here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in order to prove to us that you are going to be a good girl-- and we want to keep you here-- please obey to the rules.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, Mama, I'll do anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I will not cry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I will not do anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not-- no-- nothing, so-- which happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We sat in that room, and when you talk about the story of Anne Frank, this is where my story comes in, too.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because that room was lived in from morning to night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only time that was when we had to go to the toilet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If the coast was clear, downstairs was a toilet.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
